{
  "stem": "6777.1",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But the auntie and her daughter, Julia, they got, they didn't get as far in the second World War as in the first one.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They also fled the Germans, but they fled through Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the Germans caught up with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And also, they Have not been anymore Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because they had to-- since the husband was sick in Moscow in the first World War, and Jews--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This one.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I put it back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where do you want me to start from?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in the first--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Can you stop for a moment, because-- [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, in the first World War, Jews have not been allowed to stay in Moscow.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And since her husband was sick and she had the baby boy, they had to become Christian.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the second World War, she again fled to German.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But this time, not toward Moscow, but towards Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the Germans caught up with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And because they have been Jewish by birth, the auntie and the daughter of her-- Maria and the daughter, Julia-- have been hanged in the square of a small town as a warning to other Jews.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the boy, Alex, he was already taken into the Russian Army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He survived.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He survived the war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, after the war, he found us in [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my adopted grandma gave him all sorts of things, because he had a wife and a baby.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I didn't-- I hadn't been at home when he came, although I know that he survived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I haven't had any more parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Grandparents?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To the Polish government gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I haven't been in any primary school.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was private tuition for two years and then straight into the first year.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Straight into, into primary school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the primary school was government-run, is that?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
